Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.73,0:00:03.65,Italics,Na,0000,0000,0000,,In hopes of saving the kids,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.65,0:00:06.21,Italics,Na,0000,0000,0000,,Rimuru took them in search \Nof the Dwelling of Spirits.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.21,0:00:08.71,Italics,Na,0000,0000,0000,,On the way, they met Ramiris, \Nthe Queen of Spirits.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.26,0:00:11.92,Italics,Na,0000,0000,0000,,Then, after earning her agreement to help,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.92,0:00:14.71,Italics,Na,0000,0000,0000,,they set out to try to \Nsummon superior spirits.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.51,0:00:18.72,Flashback,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,So this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.32,0:00:22.71,Flashback,Ramiris,0000,0000,0000,,The deepest part of the Labyrinth, \Nthe Dwelling of Spirits.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.67,0:00:28.05,Flashback,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Kenya, Ryota, Gale, Alice, Chloe...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.52,0:00:29.35,Flashback,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.35,0:00:29.81,Flashback,Kids,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.89,0:00:36.20,Flashback_Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Shizu-san, wherever you \Nare, are you watching?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.17,0:00:38.71,Flashback_Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make sure
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.57,0:00:41.39,Flashback_Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,your wish is realized.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.53,0:02:11.99,Show_Title,Title,0000,0000,0000,,That {\c&H471E13&}Time {\c&HCD9612&}I Got {\c&H471E13&}Reincarnated {\c&HCD9612&}as a {\c&H7E4F0A&}Slime
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.41,0:02:16.58,Ep_Title,Title,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1400,518)}Episode 23: Saved Souls
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.18,0:02:22.91,Main,Ramiris,0000,0000,0000,,Now, listen. You'll call to \Nthe spirits from over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.91,0:02:23.75,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,What do we say?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.94,0:02:28.01,Main,Ramiris,0000,0000,0000,,Anything. It can be, "Help me!" \NOr even, "Let's play!"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.38,0:02:31.76,Main,Ramiris,0000,0000,0000,,If any spirits take interest and come \Nto you, the summon was a success.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.49,0:02:34.44,Main,Ryota,0000,0000,0000,,Will they actually come?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.03,0:02:36.37,Main,Kenya,0000,0000,0000,,Sure they will!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.37,0:02:37.43,Main,Ryota,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.67,0:02:39.54,Main,Kenya,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, they'll come, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.54,0:02:40.94,Main,Chloe,0000,0000,0000,,They'll come?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.11,0:02:44.02,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be fine. In the worst case...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.43,0:02:46.68,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tame a demon if I have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.68,0:02:48.69,Main,Ramiris,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, your face looks really evil right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.89,0:02:51.91,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,So, who's going first?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.64,0:02:54.66,Main,Gale,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.17,0:02:58.51,Main,Gale,0000,0000,0000,,If anything happens to me, take care of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.71,0:03:06.21,Main,Ramiris,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wait to see what \Nkind of spirit shows up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.85,0:03:10.86,Main,Gale,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'm going to pray now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.40,0:03:42.46,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,These aren't superior spirits... \NThey're inferior spirits.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.75,0:03:45.66,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,If these tiny spirits
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.66,0:03:49.34,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,are fragments cut from a great \Nspirit by Gale's prayer,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.62,0:03:52.18,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,then we just need to create a new spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.74,0:03:53.47,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Great Sage.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.16,0:03:55.11,Italics_Top,Great Sage,0000,0000,0000,,Question.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.11,0:03:58.99,Italics_Top,Great Sage,0000,0000,0000,,Use Gluttony to consume \Nand unify the spirits?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.68,0:03:59.72,sign_1407_3_Tokyo__Present_D,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1400,1)\bord0\c&HDEE5E4&}Unify the spirits?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.72,0:04:01.28,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,That's a yes, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.66,0:04:03.83,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Gale, keep praying.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.02,0:04:11.56,Main,Ramiris,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.56,0:04:14.08,Main,Ramiris,0000,0000,0000,,You ate them?! How could you do that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.08,0:04:16.45,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Keep quiet and watch. I have an idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.13,0:04:18.58,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Go for it, Great Sage.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.84,0:04:19.66,Italics_Top,Great Sage,0000,0000,0000,,Notice.
