Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.63,0:04:36.84,sign_6207_48_Notice,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\pos(184,180)\fad(903,1)}Earth\N{\fs16}Artificial\NSuperior Spirit
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.63,0:04:36.84,sign_6207_48_Notice,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(436,130)\fad(445,1)}Gale Gibson
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.51,0:04:36.84,sign_6207_48_Notice,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(436,228)}Unify?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.99,0:04:36.84,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.66,0:04:45.94,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,How's this? Appraisal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.51,0:04:51.10,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,His rampant energy is calming down.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.72,0:04:52.90,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,He's got control.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.97,0:04:56.29,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Now, as his body matures,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.29,0:04:58.93,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,he should gradually acquire abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.68,0:05:01.49,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,We did it, Great Sage!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.49,0:05:02.50,Italics_Top,Great Sage,0000,0000,0000,,Heh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.90,0:05:06.12,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like I just saw Great\NSage make a smug face...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.12,0:05:07.09,Italics_Top,Great Sage,0000,0000,0000,,You imagined it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.18,0:05:10.92,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, it's over. You did great.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.30,0:05:12.10,Main,Gale,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.88,0:05:15.80,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,You're okay now. The destruction's stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.80,0:05:16.68,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,I guarantee it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.14,0:05:20.80,Main,Gale,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sensei... Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.27,0:05:24.81,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Think nothing of it. It's only natural \Nthat I'd protect my students.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.39,0:05:27.29,Main,Kenya,0000,0000,0000,,Hooray!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.29,0:05:28.73,Main,Ryota,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.49,0:05:28.73,Main,Alice,0000,0000,0000,,You did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.54,0:05:30.40,Main,Chloe,0000,0000,0000,,That's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.69,0:05:32.73,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,It's too soon to celebrate.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.73,0:05:35.15,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Save the parties for after \Nyou're all successful.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.85,0:05:49.59,Italics_Top,Great Sage,0000,0000,0000,,Notice.
