Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.23,0:06:02.89,Italics_Top,Great Sage,0000,0000,0000,,Unify the completed artificial superior \Nspirit of space with Alice Rondo?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.89,0:06:03.60,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.49,0:06:11.22,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Alice, you did great.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.22,0:06:12.52,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be okay now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.79,0:06:15.90,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Well, thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.25,0:06:22.53,Main,Kenya,0000,0000,0000,,All right! I'm next!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.95,0:06:27.95,Main,Kenya,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't even started praying yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.55,0:06:31.75,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Is something coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.01,0:06:38.65,Main,Light,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! How are ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.65,0:06:40.22,Main,Light,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just great!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.63,0:06:43.21,Main,Ramiris,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck are you doing in my house?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.21,0:06:45.01,Main,Light,0000,0000,0000,,It was just a whim.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.01,0:06:46.68,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Who is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.68,0:06:47.43,Main,Ramiris,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.43,0:06:50.89,Main,Light,0000,0000,0000,,Hiya! I'm a light spirit! Nice to meet ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.89,0:06:53.71,Main,Light,0000,0000,0000,,Unlike the evil spirit that\Nfell to become this monster
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.71,0:06:55.77,Main,Light,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a pure, innocent spirit of light!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.77,0:06:56.98,Main,Ramiris,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you calling evil?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.31,0:07:01.79,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Kenya, it looks like you summoned \Na superior spirit of light.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.79,0:07:03.32,Main,Kenya,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.71,0:07:06.81,Main,Light,0000,0000,0000,,So your name's Kenya? \NOkay, I'm gonna call you Ken!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.81,0:07:09.72,Main,Light,0000,0000,0000,,I could just feel something shining in you, Ken!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.72,0:07:11.46,Main,Light,0000,0000,0000,,I know, 'cause I'm light!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.22,0:07:13.75,Main,Kenya,0000,0000,0000,,That wasn't funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.15,0:07:17.64,Main,Light,0000,0000,0000,,So on that note, I'm gonna save you, Ken!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.64,0:07:20.88,Main,Light,0000,0000,0000,,I'll look out for you \Nuntil you're all grown up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.18,0:07:24.76,Main,Light,0000,0000,0000,,You might even become a Hero, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.08,0:07:26.26,Main,Kenya,0000,0000,0000,,A Hero?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.70,0:07:27.97,Main,Ryota,0000,0000,0000,,Ken, a Hero?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.97,0:07:28.77,Main,Gale,0000,0000,0000,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.44,0:07:31.03,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that would be something...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.92,0:07:35.79,Main,Ramiris,0000,0000,0000,,It inhabited you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.79,0:07:36.50,Main,Kenya,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.50,0:07:38.00,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,That easily?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.68,0:07:39.61,Main,Kenya,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.03,0:07:40.76,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.40,0:07:44.42,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah! It's fine! All according to plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.60,0:07:46.76,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Good for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.76,0:07:48.75,Main,Kenya,0000,0000,0000,,Er, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.60,0:07:50.42,Main,Kenya,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
