Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.88,0:08:04.93,Italics_Top,Great Sage,0000,0000,0000,,Unify it with Ryota Sekiguchi?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.93,0:08:05.97,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.45,0:08:09.76,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Just one left.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.94,0:08:19.44,Main,Chloe,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, um... Sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.50,0:08:27.20,Main,Chloe,0000,0000,0000,,Um, Sensei... um...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.82,0:08:31.08,Main,Chloe,0000,0000,0000,,I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.74,0:08:32.96,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I like you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.74,0:08:39.04,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,I wish you'd waited another eight... \Nno, ten years to say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.01,0:08:42.49,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Hell, I wish I'd heard \Nthat while I was alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.44,0:08:45.10,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Go on and pray.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.10,0:08:45.92,Main,Chloe,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.97,0:08:52.89,Main,Ramiris,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.57,0:09:01.40,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,That pressure... \NIt felt like the sky fell down.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.13,0:09:16.12,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,That's... not a spirit?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.49,0:09:17.45,Italics_Top,Great Sage,0000,0000,0000,,Answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.45,0:09:20.52,Italics_Top,Great Sage,0000,0000,0000,,It is a spiritual body equivalent \Nto a superior spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.52,0:09:22.88,Italics_Top,Great Sage,0000,0000,0000,,Abnormal level of energy detected.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.06,0:09:25.42,Italics_Top,Great Sage,0000,0000,0000,,Its threshold is immeasurable.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.87,0:09:40.81,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.06,0:09:45.59,Main,Ramiris,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it! No way, no how!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.59,0:09:47.07,Main,Ramiris,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not letting you have your way!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.45,0:09:48.47,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what the heck are youâ€”
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.47,0:09:51.58,Main,Ramiris,0000,0000,0000,,Quiet! That thing's dangerous! \NCan't you see that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.82,0:09:54.33,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,How the hell would I know?! \NWhat's so dangerous?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.33,0:09:55.53,Main,Ramiris,0000,0000,0000,,We'll talk later!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.91,0:10:06.47,Main,Ramiris,0000,0000,0000,,It inhabited her!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.47,0:10:08.09,Main,Ramiris,0000,0000,0000,,Darn it! It's too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.31,0:10:11.03,Main,Ramiris,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm done! \NDon't blame me for whatever happens!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.93,0:10:13.43,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Appraisal.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.43,0:10:18.94,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,That immense energy has \Ncompletely disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.56,0:10:22.06,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,She seems... stable.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.06,0:10:24.44,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like there's no problem...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.35,0:10:27.24,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,But what in the world...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.95,0:10:31.93,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,So just what was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.93,0:10:34.92,Main,Ramiris,0000,0000,0000,,No idea! I don't know the details!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.92,0:10:37.87,Main,Ramiris,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm pretty sure that \None was born in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.87,0:10:38.46,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.62,0:10:41.71,Main,Ramiris,0000,0000,0000,,It's something resembling a spirit, \Nexcept it came from the future!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.07,0:10:43.61,Main,Ramiris,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost impossible to believe,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.61,0:10:47.37,Main,Ramiris,0000,0000,0000,,but by inhabiting her, it laid the \Nfoundation for its own rebirth?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.49,0:10:49.71,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.71,0:10:52.20,Main,Ramiris,0000,0000,0000,,I seriously don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.20,0:10:54.74,Main,Ramiris,0000,0000,0000,,But that thing had enormous power!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.74,0:10:58.35,Main,Ramiris,0000,0000,0000,,I'm pretty sure it'll be big trouble \Nif that thing is born in the future!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.35,0:11:01.73,Main,Ramiris,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it had the divine protection \Nof the Great Spirit of Time...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.11,0:11:03.71,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm completely lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.53,0:11:08.83,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,But it's all good. As long as Chloe's \Nokay, that's all that matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.83,0:11:12.59,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,No one knows what'll happen in the \Nfuture, so it means nothing right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.99,0:11:19.69,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Good for you, Chloe. \NIt went just as I planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.69,0:11:21.83,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,You're out of danger now, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.25,0:11:25.58,Main,Chloe,0000,0000,0000,,Was that really just as you planned it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.58,0:11:28.51,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah! Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.93,0:11:33.67,Main,Ramiris,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, not that it matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.67,0:11:37.24,Main,Ramiris,0000,0000,0000,,Now that it's inhabited her, \Nit's out of my control.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.24,0:11:40.43,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,What's the problem? \NEveryone was successful.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.78,0:11:44.44,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks! These kids are saved, thanks to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.82,0:11:46.02,Main,Chloe,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.83,0:11:48.50,Main,Kids,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.50,0:11:49.44,Main,Ranga,0000,0000,0000,,I'm grateful!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.21,0:11:53.45,Main,Ramiris,0000,0000,0000,,C-Cut that out already!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.45,0:11:57.87,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,And this is a Demon Lord? \NWhat has the world come to?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.84,0:12:16.39,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,I did it, Shizu-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.90,0:12:18.73,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,They'll be okay now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.92,0:12:23.45,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,It was a happy ending!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.45,0:12:26.28,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Or so I thought, but after that...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.28,0:12:30.53,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,I had to give Ramiris a replacement \Nfor the golem I destroyed...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.66,0:12:39.47,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Then I had to summon a demon and \Nmake it possess that golem...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.02,0:12:42.08,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,And there was one last struggle.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.85,0:12:45.46,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,But hey, that's a different story.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.48,0:12:50.30,Main,Yuuki,0000,0000,0000,,I truly thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.59,0:12:53.55,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, no worries, no worries!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.05,0:12:56.03,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,The kids will be fine now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.03,0:12:58.85,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Guess they'll be able to \Nlive normal lives, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.85,0:12:59.92,Main,Yuuki,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.92,0:13:03.43,Main,Yuuki,0000,0000,0000,,It's unlikely the nations that abandoned \Nthem will ever try to take them back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.98,0:13:06.97,Main,Yuuki,0000,0000,0000,,That would violate international law, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.97,0:13:10.57,Main,Yuuki,0000,0000,0000,,They'd be making enemies of the \NFree Union if they did that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.97,0:13:14.82,Main,Yuuki,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to give the kids IDs \Nand make them members of the Union?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.50,0:13:20.58,Main,Yuuki,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if that's what they want, \Nthat might be a very good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.44,0:13:24.95,Main,Yuuki,0000,0000,0000,,But for the time being, I'd like to \Nlet them study at the Freedom Academy
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.95,0:13:27.41,Main,Yuuki,0000,0000,0000,,and give them the chance \Nto choose their future.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.41,0:13:29.08,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.52,0:13:30.90,Main,Yuuki,0000,0000,0000,,You needn't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.69,0:13:36.84,Main,Yuuki,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, you still won't tell \Nme how you resolved all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.66,0:13:39.10,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,That's a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.10,0:13:41.25,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,There are some things you don't need to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.25,0:13:44.58,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,It's no substitute for telling you,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.58,0:13:47.73,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,but I hope you'll be content with this...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.02,0:13:53.23,Main,Yuuki,0000,0000,0000,,Understood! Thank you, Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.16,0:14:02.17,Main,Kenya,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.10,0:14:15.17,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,So much has happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.26,0:17:22.43,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,But now this case is closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.86,0:17:24.96,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,All of our problems have been solved.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.81,0:17:29.76,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Shizu-san, this is for the best, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.93,0:17:39.29,Italics,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Slime-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.17,0:19:18.98,Main,Diablo,0000,0000,0000,,What a horrible blunder.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.65,0:19:22.08,Main,Diablo,0000,0000,0000,,You finally summoned me,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.49,0:19:25.23,Main,Diablo,0000,0000,0000,,and my own family got ahead of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.38,0:19:29.83,Main,Diablo,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, without a doubt...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.45,0:19:36.99,Main,Diablo,0000,0000,0000,,I know you will lead me to \Nthe truth of this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.78,0:19:50.01,Main,Chloe,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei... Sensei, don't go...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.29,0:19:54.15,Main,Ryota,0000,0000,0000,,Chlo-chi... Don't try to keep Sensei here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.15,0:19:56.92,Main,Alice,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Just get going already!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.92,0:19:57.76,Main,Chloe,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.05,0:20:06.02,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Take care of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.32,0:20:08.61,Main,Yuuki,0000,0000,0000,,I will. You can count on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.13,0:20:15.20,Main,Chloe,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.47,0:20:25.18,Main,Kenya,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez, Chloe, you're such a crybaby.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.18,0:20:26.33,Main,Kenya,0000,0000,0000,,Stop crying!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.50,0:20:28.00,Main,Ryota,0000,0000,0000,,You're crying, too, Ken-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.00,0:20:30.00,Main,Kenya,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not! My eyes are just sweating!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.31,0:20:32.76,Main,Chloe,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei... Sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.82,0:20:37.89,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Chloe.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.70,0:20:40.26,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,There, there, Chloe.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.70,0:20:43.06,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you this, so cheer up, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.38,0:20:46.52,Main,Alice,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted that, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.36,0:20:48.65,Main,Chloe,0000,0000,0000,,But I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.81,0:20:50.33,Main,Kenya,0000,0000,0000,,Lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.33,0:20:51.86,Main,Alice,0000,0000,0000,,No fair! No fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.86,0:20:54.69,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right. I have gifts for you guys, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.62,0:21:02.44,Main,Ryota,0000,0000,0000,,Ken-chan, you look awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.44,0:21:03.95,Main,Kenya,0000,0000,0000,,So do you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.95,0:21:05.37,Main,Gale,0000,0000,0000,,These are fantastic!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.00,0:21:07.88,Main,Alice,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.35,0:21:11.48,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,There's a really handy girl \Nnamed Shuna in my country.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.48,0:21:13.38,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,I had her make those and send them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.55,0:21:14.54,Main,Kenya,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.54,0:21:15.86,Main,Chloe,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.86,0:21:18.39,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Now, listen. Be sure you study hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.16,0:21:22.82,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Saying goodbye is sad, but it's \Nnot as if we'll never meet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.39,0:21:26.61,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,I'll bring Ranga and come visit you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.36,0:21:30.52,Main,Ranga,0000,0000,0000,,Be sure to keep up with your studies, \Neven after we leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.76,0:21:33.49,Main,Kenya,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You'd better come visit us!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.49,0:21:37.78,Main,Alice,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-When I graduate, I might \Njust come visit you, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.02,0:21:39.77,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Sure. I'll be waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.77,0:21:43.10,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have the entire city \Nof Rimuru welcome you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.43,0:21:49.38,Main,Kenya,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.38,0:21:50.30,Main,Ryota,0000,0000,0000,,See you again!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.30,0:21:52.05,Main,Alice,0000,0000,0000,,Take care!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.30,0:21:52.05,Main,Gale,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.82,0:21:54.55,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Be well!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.61,0:22:01.62,Main,Chloe,0000,0000,0000,,See you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.40,0:22:09.90,Main,Ranga,0000,0000,0000,,Master, why did you give \Nher your treasured mask?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.50,0:22:13.40,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I wonder why, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.69,0:22:18.31,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure either,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.31,0:22:22.69,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,but for some reason, giving it to Chloe \Nfelt like the natural thing to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.47,0:22:25.16,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Something told me that was best.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.82,0:22:27.16,Main,Ranga,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.61,0:22:32.54,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,I bet Shizu-san would be happier \Nwith Chloe having it than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.15,0:22:35.80,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,She'll take good care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.80,0:22:38.33,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,She might even follow in Shizu-san's \Nfootsteps to become a hero...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.33,0:22:41.46,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Heck, she might even become a Hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.46,0:22:42.05,Main,Ranga,0000,0000,0000,,Surely not!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.27,0:22:46.07,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Ranga!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.07,0:22:47.76,Main,Ranga,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.28,0:22:51.24,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go back to our town... to our home!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.24,0:22:52.58,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.66,0:23:08.16,Italics,Na,0000,0000,0000,,The man who thought he was living \Na perfectly ordinary life
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.45,0:23:10.65,Italics,Na,0000,0000,0000,,was stabbed by a random attacker and died,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.65,0:23:12.87,Italics,Na,0000,0000,0000,,and was reincarnated in another world.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.77,0:23:15.48,Italics,Na,0000,0000,0000,,He took in the Storm Dragon Veldora
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.48,0:23:19.49,Italics,Na,0000,0000,0000,,as well as the will and \Nbody of a certain girl,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.49,0:23:21.55,Italics,Na,0000,0000,0000,,overcame many crises,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.55,0:23:23.72,Italics,Na,0000,0000,0000,,brought together many races of monsters,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.97,0:23:26.77,Italics,Na,0000,0000,0000,,built a nation, and saved \Na group of children.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.35,0:23:31.01,Italics,Na,0000,0000,0000,,His name is Rimuru Tempest,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.01,0:23:33.29,Italics,Na,0000,0000,0000,,and he is but a slime.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.95,0:23:39.36,Italics_Top,Great Sage,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, "Extra: Black and a Mask."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.15,0:23:40.03,Next_Ep_Title,Title,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(900,1)}Extra:{\u1\c&HDCE3DB&\bord0} Black and a Mask

